  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/594350/extras/50990733781aee81d802c1e8951b881b.avif?t=1766146651\" width=612 height=272 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>As a person who identifies as an attack helicopter, your daily activities may include, morning maintenance, aerial attack runs, and delivering hell-fire missiles on noncombatants for democracy.<br>Or you know, <strong>dating other helicopters</strong>. It is a visual novel after all...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/594350/extras/835875e239be7e8e35d83b57988636f9.avif?t=1766146651\" width=612 height=272 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DETAILS</h2>Attack Helicopter Dating Simulator is made by the uruguayans at <strong>Curse Box Studios</strong>. Hilariously written and with a bunch or routes and eleven endings (where you probably don't die or generate a crippling addiction to helicopter s*x), Attack Helicopter Dating Simulator is guaranteed likely to bring you joy for numerous playthroughs!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/594350/extras/04526114aab9dbefaeee52a416760dd0.avif?t=1766146651\" width=612 height=272 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Join the Airforce.<br></li><li>See the <span class=\"bb_strike\">World</span> Darkest Depths of Your Frail Mat Sack Existence.<br></li><li>Meet Fun and Interesting <span class=\"bb_strike\">People</span> Helicopters that won't get us sued by the manufacturers I swear (plz).<br></li><li><span class=\"bb_strike\">Date</span> Perform aerial strafing maneuvers against them.<br></li><li>Kill in the name  of <span class=\"bb_strike\">the military industrial complex</span> your county<br></li><li>It's a respectful tribute to Helicopter-gendered individuals.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/594350/extras/cd3dddec3d4de70a4244c69a9ed9270a.avif?t=1766146651\" width=612 height=272 /></span>",
